(1 clic)
</li>
<li class="link" data-url="/redaction/links/63923/modifier" id="link_63923" lang="en">
<a class="hit_counter" data-hit="63923" href="http://europa.eu/rapid/pressReleasesAction.do?reference=MEMO/09/439&amp;format=HTML&amp;aged=0&amp;language=EN&amp;guiLanguage=en" hreflang="en" title="http://europa.eu/rapid/pressReleasesAction.do?reference=MEMO/09/439&amp;format=HTML&amp;aged=0&amp;language=EN&amp;guiLanguage=en">Communiqué de presse de la commission Européenne</a>
